data.description: Minutes from PAX River Naval Air Station, you’ll find this wonderful abode consisting of 6 bedrooms 4 full bathrooms plus an office area with lots of open space! Generous master bedroom with large bathroom. The fully finished downstairs has a private entry and exit with a paved exterior walkway to the driveway. Great in-law or investment ADU rental opportunity! The driveway has also been expanded and can hold up to 5 cars without taking into consideration the large 2-car garage. Check out the 3d tour available. This is a great home for a good family. Schedule your appointment today!
